<a name="why"></a>
<div class="container-yellow">
	<div class="container">
		<div class="row text-center">
			<div class="col-md-12">
				<h1>Why JC Auto</h1>
				<p class="intro">
					With more than <%= Date.today.year - 1978 %> years in the industry, we like to think our work speaks for itself. However, we also take pride in our ability to serve our customers with a smile. We hold ourselves to high standards of service and customer care. Much of our service work and parts sales is through mail order, and we welcome customers from across the country, as well as internationally.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class= "col-sm-4 col-md-4" >
				<%= link_to "/policies" do %><%= image_tag "master/customer-service.png", alt: "Customer Service", onmouseover: "document.getElementById('tech1').src='#{asset_path("master/customer-service-hover.png")}'", onmouseout: "document.getElementById('tech1').src='#{asset_path("master/customer-service.png")}'", class:"icon", id:"tech1" %><% end %>
				<!--%= image_tag "master/Tech.png", onmouseover: "this.src='#{asset_path('master/Tech-hover.png')}'", onmouseout: "this.src='#{asset_path('master/Tech.png')}'", class:"icon" %-->
				<h3>Customer Service</h3>
				<p>We've put policies in place to guarantee that we work with you in a respectful and friendly way to get your project just how you like it. Restoring your car should be fun and enjoyable. No matter what your background or level of expertise, we strive to work with you to make the restoration process as easy as possible.</p>
				<!-- Change Tech image on hover -->
				<%= link_to "Our Policies >", "/policies", class: "button-link", onmouseover:"document.getElementById('tech1').src='#{asset_path('master/customer-service-hover.png')}'", onmouseout:"document.getElementById('tech1').src='#{asset_path('master/customer-service.png')}'" %>

			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-4 col-md-4">
				<%= link_to "/timeline" do %><%= image_tag "master/history.png", alt: "Our History", onmouseover: "document.getElementById('tech2').src='#{asset_path("master/history-hover.png")}'", onmouseout: "document.getElementById('tech2').src='#{asset_path("master/history.png")}'", class:"icon", id:"tech2" %><% end %>
				<h3>Our History</h3>
				<p>Jeff started working on cars with his father at a young age. He soon grew independent, taking on projects of his own and learning ever since. Now, he and his wife Lisa are proud owners of multiple project cars, and enjoy running their own shop. We are proud of our rich history and enjoy working with our customers!</p>
				<!-- Change Tech image on hover -->
				<%= link_to "JC Auto Timeline >", "/timeline", class:"button-link", onmouseover: "document.getElementById('tech2').src='#{asset_path('master/history-hover.png')}'", onmouseout: "document.getElementById('tech2').src='#{asset_path('master/history.png')}'" %>
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-4 col-md-4">
				<%= link_to "/gallery" do %><%= image_tag "master/work.png", alt: "Our Work", onmouseover: "document.getElementById('tech3').src='#{asset_path("master/work-hover.png")}'", onmouseout: "document.getElementById('tech3').src='#{asset_path("master/work.png")}'", class:"icon", id:"tech3" %><% end %>
				<h3>Our Experience</h3>
				<p>Our long list of past projects can speak to our attention to detail and the broad spectrum of work that we have taken on. We take pride in the work we do and the precision and beauty of a job well done. Browse some of the cars we have worked on in the past, and those in progress.</p>
				<%= link_to "Pictures of Our Work >", "/gallery", class:"button-link", onmouseover: "document.getElementById('tech3').src='#{asset_path('master/work-hover.png')}'", onmouseout: "document.getElementById('tech3').src='#{asset_path('master/work.png')}'" %>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

<a name="who"></a>
