	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-md-12" style="text-align: center">
			<h1>Who We Are</h1>
			<p class="intro">We are lucky to have such a wide range of skillsets at our shop. Nevertheless, we do have a lot in common including, of course, our love of MoPars and Big E Ales.</p>
		</div>
